title: Travel time estimates
text:
Travel time estimates for the John Nolen Drive corridor between Rimrock and the “Hairball” (JND/Wilson/Willy/Blair). Note that for this route, the shortest duration route is shown even when that involves not taking JND itself but an alternative route.

title: About
text:
This website displays the data from the analysis of travel time estimates in select Madison (Wisconsin) corridors. The data is pulled from the Google Routes API. The main repository for the project is at https://github.com/vgXhc/travel_time_estimates
A blog post about the initial concept is available here
Author/contact: Harald Kliems (kliems@proton.me)
